Items.Title: Executive Session - Part 2 - Disciplinary Matter Regarding Council Member Jennings.
Items.ActionText: This Oversight was Hearing Held by Committee
Items.MatterName: Disciplinary Matter Regarding Council Member Jennings - Part 2

Items.Title: Resolution calling upon the Council of the City of New York to adopt the recommendation made by the Committee on Standards and Ethics that no penalty be imposed against Council Member Allan W. Jennings for his actions occurring at the Stated Meeting held on February 4, 2004.
Items.ActionName: Hearing on P-C Item by Comm
Items.ActionText: This Resolution was Hearing on P-C Item by Comm
Items.MatterName: Adopt the recommendation made by the Committee on Standards and Ethics that no penalty be imposed against Council Member Allan W. Jennings for his actions occurring at the Stated Meeting held on February 4, 2004.
